=======================

This is XNeko.
I have added color and root capability to this app.
I had nothing to do with anything except these modifications.
Don't look at the code.

-----------------------
 INSTALLATION
-----------------------
% make
Dat's it.

-----------------------
 HELP
-----------------------
% xneko -help
Dat's it.

-----------------------
 COLORS
-----------------------
% xneko -bg <background> -fg <foreground>
Dat's it.

-----------------------
 ROOTWINDOW OPS
-----------------------
% xneko -root
Dat's it.

Enjoy.

Dan Checkoway   8/4/94
